'''Lucy Gordon''' (May 22 1980-May 20 2009) was an [[United Kingdom|English]] [[movie]] actress and model who worked for CoverGirl 1997. She starred in ''The Four Feathers'' and ''Spider-Man 3''. Gordon passed away in [[Paris, France]] by hanging in her flat.
